deck: One day I came across on the Internet in a letter that according to custom of the Japanese pilots at the end of World War II, a kamikaze wrote to his father. This letter fighter pilot "Zero", sacrificing life in order to sink the American ship, expressed his last wishes, making a kind of testament. Inspired by this letter, I decided to create a story about the Japanese kamikaze.
description: The Second World War. A nightmare that  will be remembered not only us numerous casualties, but  the deeds of ordinary people. This comic is dedicated to  the four pilots who fought in 4 different armies: the Japanese, German, American and Soviet. What motivated them?  Whether they were the heroes of the circumstances, fanatics or adventurers? The authors do not give any estimates, they just show us the ordinary people caught in extreme situations, which exhibit  their heroism.
name: The Final Flight
